# PocketBase binary + runtime data — never commit to public repo
# The binary is platform-specific (macOS ARM64); pb_data contains personal job application data
pocketbase/pocketbase
pocketbase/CHANGELOG.md
pocketbase/LICENSE.md
pocketbase/pb_data/
# Keep pb_migrations tracked (schema migrations are safe to publish)
!pocketbase/pb_migrations/

# DB backups — committed by backup.yml GitHub Action (one zip per day from PocketHost)
# backups/ is intentionally NOT ignored — zip files are tracked in git for restore history
